Function Reference/wp delete object term relationships « WordPress Codex
-----------

Will unlink the object from the taxonomy or taxonomies. Will remove all
relationships between the object and any terms in a particular taxonomy
or taxonomies. Does not remove the term or the taxonomy itself.

Usage
-----

` <?php wp_delete_object_term_relationships( $object_id, $taxonomies ); ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$object_id` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) The term Object ID that refers to the term.
    Default: *None*

 `$taxonomies` 
:   ([*string|array*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String.7Carray "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) List of Taxonomy Names or single Taxonomy name.
    Default: *None*

\

